"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1938572-Olympics-Matt-Richardson-Team-GB-ban\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Matthew Richardson could be handed a two-year ban from cycling following his shock defection toTeam GB.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 105, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 20, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Richardson_(footballer)\", \"score\": 0.9918787924836031, \"rank\": 0.007602339181287399, \"text\": \"Matthew Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13414980\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Richardson_(footballer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matthew_Richardson_(footballer)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a two-year ban\", \"from\": 35, \"to\": 49}, {\"ngram\": \"cycling\", \"from\": 55, \"to\": 62}, {\"ngram\": \"his shock defection\", \"from\": 73, \"to\": 92}, {\"ngram\": \"GB\", \"from\": 100, \"to\": 102}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The cyclist, who took three medals at the recent Paris Games for Australia,announced his attention to switch allegiances earlier this week.\", \"from\": 107, \"to\": 246, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 172, \"end\": 181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9994323751700471, \"rank\": 0.00040425960233436714, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The cyclist\", \"from\": 107, \"to\": 118}, {\"ngram\": \"three medals\", \"from\": 129, \"to\": 141}, {\"ngram\": \"the recent Paris Games\", \"from\": 145, \"to\": 167}, {\"ngram\": \"his attention\", \"from\": 192, \"to\": 205}, {\"ngram\": \"allegiances\", \"from\": 216, \"to\": 227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It comes just days after he made theOlympicpodium in the French capital on three occasions, with cycling chiefs at AusCycling reported to have been left stunned by the decision.\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 305, \"end\": 311, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9938895016881325, \"rank\": 0.005913314619429663, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 363, \"end\": 373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AusCycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AusCycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AusCycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/AusCycling\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theOlympicpodium\", \"from\": 281, \"to\": 297}, {\"ngram\": \"three occasions\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 338}, {\"ngram\": \"cycling chiefs\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 359}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 412, \"to\": 424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So much so, that the Australian officials could explore a clause that would see Richardson banned from competing for Team GB until 2026.\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 563, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 448, \"end\": 458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.8247313871947568, \"rank\": 0.14279521381346952, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 507, \"end\": 517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999984006566649, \"rank\": 1.5993458422597712e-06, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a clause\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 491}, {\"ngram\": \"Team GB\", \"from\": 544, \"to\": 551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking after the defection, AusCycling's executive general manager, Jesse Korf said: \\\"There is disappointment around the decision and the process and not knowing around Matt's circumstances.\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 757, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the defection\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 593}, {\"ngram\": \"Jesse Korf\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 645}, {\"ngram\": \"disappointment\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 676}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 696}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 712}, {\"ngram\": \"Matt's circumstances\", \"from\": 736, \"to\": 756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For sure he will not compete at the upcoming world championships [in October].\", \"from\": 759, \"to\": 838, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the upcoming world championships\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 824}, {\"ngram\": \"October\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 836}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But the non-competition duration and clauses, that is being interrogated and looked into at the moment together with the UCI and ASC (Australian Sports Commission).\\\"\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 1006, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 962, \"end\": 965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"score\": 0.999991790625518, \"rank\": 7.724322530547494e-06, \"text\": \"UCI\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\"}, {\"begin\": 970, \"end\": 973, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Society_of_Cinematographers\", \"score\": 0.9660423223826007, \"rank\": 0.022409149221099822, \"text\": \"ASC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Society_of_Cinematographers\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Society_of_Cinematographers\"}, {\"begin\": 975, \"end\": 1003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian Sports Commission\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sport_Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the non-competition duration\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 873}, {\"ngram\": \"clauses\", \"from\": 878, \"to\": 885}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He continued: \\\"That is something that we would have to discuss internally because we obviously have a big say in that and we need to review that\\u2026 \\\"So that would have to be a conversation to get to a joint decision [with the stakeholders] before we can share that and start a conversation with UCI and Matt and British Cycling.\\\"\", \"from\": 1008, \"to\": 1338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1304, \"end\": 1307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"score\": 0.999991790625518, \"rank\": 7.724322530547494e-06, \"text\": \"UCI\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Union_Cycliste_Internationale\"}, {\"begin\": 1321, \"end\": 1336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1040}, {\"ngram\": \"a big say\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1117}, {\"ngram\": \"a conversation\", \"from\": 1180, \"to\": 1194}, {\"ngram\": \"a joint decision\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"the stakeholders\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1244}, {\"ngram\": \"a conversation\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1295}, {\"ngram\": \"UCI\", \"from\": 1301, \"to\": 1304}, {\"ngram\": \"Matt\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1313}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Richardson was British-born but had moved to Australia at an early age and has competed under the Australian flag ever since breaking into the sport.\", \"from\": 1340, \"to\": 1489, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"score\": 0.9999984006566649, \"rank\": 1.5993458422597712e-06, \"text\": \"Richardson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Samuel_Richardson\"}, {\"begin\": 1385, \"end\": 1394, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9994323751700471, \"rank\": 0.00040425960233436714, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1438, \"end\": 1453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Australian flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an early age\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1410}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He finished the Games as Australia's most successful cyclist in Paris, but has cited a 'childhood dream' of competing for Team GB as the reason for his shock switch.\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1516, \"end\": 1525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9994323751700471, \"rank\": 0.00040425960233436714, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 1555, \"end\": 1560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999996990277848, \"rank\": 3.0097235368434893e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1512}, {\"ngram\": \"a 'childhood dream\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1594}, {\"ngram\": \"Team GB\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1620}, {\"ngram\": \"the reason\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1634}, {\"ngram\": \"his shock switch\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1655}]}, {\"sentence\": \"OnInstagram, the newest member of Team GB's cycling team said: \\\"I have made the decision to pack up my entire life and move half way across the world to begin the next chapter in my cycling career.\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1692, \"end\": 1699, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.6950377531958732, \"rank\": 0.32496847087198294, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"OnInstagram\", \"from\": 1658, \"to\": 1669}, {\"ngram\": \"the newest member\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1688}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1746}, {\"ngram\": \"my entire life\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1772}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1807}, {\"ngram\": \"the next chapter\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1833}, {\"ngram\": \"my cycling career\", \"from\": 1837, \"to\": 1854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is with a sense of excitement and renewal I announce I have joined the Great British Cycling Team.\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1957, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1936, \"end\": 1951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Cycling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Cycling\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sense\", \"from\": 1867, \"to\": 1874}, {\"ngram\": \"excitement\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 1888}, {\"ngram\": \"renewal\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1900}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Switching nationality was a difficult decision, and not one I took lightly.\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 2037, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Switching nationality\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 1983}, {\"ngram\": \"a difficult decision\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 2008}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a personal choice, made after careful consideration of my career and future.\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2121, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a personal choice\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"careful consideration\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2096}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2109}, {\"ngram\": \"future\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2120}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not something I decided on quickly or easily\\u2026 We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2283, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2140}, {\"ngram\": \"your sign-up\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2192}, {\"ngram\": \"content\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2211}, {\"ngram\": \"ways\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2219}, {\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2360, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"adverts\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2308}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"3rd parties\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2332}, {\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 2342, \"to\": 2359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2393, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any time\", \"from\": 2384, \"to\": 2392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy \\\"But this decision is about following my passion and pushing myself to new heights.\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2501, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2416}, {\"ngram\": \"this decision\", \"from\": 2422, \"to\": 2435}, {\"ngram\": \"my passion\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2465}, {\"ngram\": \"new heights\", \"from\": 2488, \"to\": 2499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not about leaving something behind, but about embracing a new chapter in my journey and chasing a dream, a dream that is to race for the country in which I was born.\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2528, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"a new chapter\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2579}, {\"ngram\": \"my journey\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2593}, {\"ngram\": \"a dream\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2613}, {\"ngram\": \"a dream\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2654}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hope you can understand and support me as I continue to give my best in the sport I love.\\\"\", \"from\": 2677, \"to\": 2770, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH CONNECT WITH US TODAY'S PAPER See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2772, \"to\": 2941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2909, \"end\": 2922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.951168552699141e-17, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_E